  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multicentric, observational, retrospective registry including patients underwent implantable
      device implantation (pacemaker or ICD) for any indication in the period from 2009 to 2016,
      followed by remote monitoring. The aims of the registry are to evaluate the occurrence of
      atrial arrhythmias, of hospitalizations, and the mortality during a long-term follow-up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
